targets.rawSql:
SELECT SUM(total_octets) FROM flows_v5_agg_5min WHERE ($__timeFilter(bucket_5min) AND
                                                        exporter IN ($exporter ) AND
                                                        protocol IN ($protocol ) AND
                                                        srcaddr IN ($srcaddr ) AND
                                                        dstaddr IN ($dstaddr ) AND 
                                                        srcport IN ($srcport ) AND 
                                                        dstport IN ($dstport ) AND 
                                                        input IN ($ifacein ) AND
                                                        output IN ($ifaceout)
                                                        ) GROUP BY exporter LIMIT 50

SELECT SUM(total_octets), $__timeGroup(bucket_5min,$__interval,NULL) AS "time" FROM flows_v5_agg_5min  WHERE ($__timeFilter(bucket_5min) AND
                                                        exporter IN ($exporter ) AND
                                                        protocol IN ($protocol ) AND
                                                        srcaddr IN ($srcaddr ) AND
                                                        dstaddr IN ($dstaddr ) AND 
                                                        srcport IN ($srcport ) AND 
                                                        dstport IN ($dstport ) AND 
                                                        input IN ($ifacein ) AND
                                                        output IN ($ifaceout)
                                                        ) GROUP BY bucket_5min ORDER BY $__timeGroup(bucket_5min,$__interval,NULL) DESC LIMIT 50

SELECT bucket_5min, exporter, srcaddr,dstaddr, srcport,dstport, protocol, input, output, total_packets, total_octets FROM flows_v5_agg_5min WHERE ($__timeFilter(bucket_5min) AND
                                                        exporter IN ($exporter ) AND
                                                        protocol IN ($protocol ) AND
                                                        srcaddr IN ($srcaddr ) AND
                                                        dstaddr IN ($dstaddr ) AND 
                                                        srcport IN ($srcport ) AND 
                                                        dstport IN ($dstport ) AND 
                                                        input IN ($ifacein ) AND
                                                        output IN ($ifaceout)
                                                        ) GROUP BY bucket_5min, exporter,srcaddr,dstaddr,srcport, dstport, protocol, input, output, total_packets, total_octets LIMIT 50
